{"tid":1988322,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"許樹昌稱現時本港約5%新型肺炎患者需入住深切治療部","createTime":"2020-04-25T06:40:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-25T06:58:58.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7fc4cf33aa5f0ed2e8d5cd13edee5567e9547380","tid":1988322,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:40:14.000Z","msg":"政府抗疫督導委員會專家顧問、中文大學醫學院呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌在一個電台節目表示，新型肺炎的傳染性強，但病情普遍較沙士輕微，現時<span style=\"color: red;\">本港大約有5%的患者需入住深切治療部，但當年沙士有四分一患者需深切治療部</span>。<br />\n<br />\n許樹昌提到，<span style=\"color: red;\">現時很多仍然留院的病人都很精神，毋須利用儀器供氧，甚至可以在病房玩電話或做運動</span>，只是等待病毒檢測呈陰性反應。<br />\n<br />\n不過他表示，目前未知道新型肺炎患者會留下什麼長期影響，<span style=\"color: red;\">病人失去味覺和嗅覺的情況都很短暫，亦只有少部分病人有肺部纖維化情況</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=5PHCsmqc8bXRSfVPwy6hKqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=a80f1bb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1522669-20200425.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=0a82252b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1522669-20200425.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>都話左疫情被誇大啦</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70636bba1bc1bb667681f4f1856bc5eb3e271641","tid":1988322,"uid":228437,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:50:02.000Z","msg":"【入黎我話你知香港點獨立】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1988323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1988323</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0a6454ba7dcdbb99b3c10f09ed034d122d5aac73","tid":1988322,"uid":1425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"香港人身體健康, 長命過中共"},{"pid":"a4e4288583ec6ba3d1c2d549bec12df95793e726","tid":1988322,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0a6454ba7dcdbb99b3c10f09ed034d122d5aac73","tid":1988322,"uid":1425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:54:49.000Z","msg":"香港人身體健康, 長命過中共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-25T06:58:58.000Z","msg":"對<br />\n同埋呢隻病毒好易被KO<br />\n呢隻肺炎應正名為廢炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}